title: 06/11/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 06/11/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's playoff games between the Bucks/Nets and the Jazz/Clippers with Jon Barry. Jon explains why he thinks the Clippers are so inconsistent. With talks of the College Football expanding to a 12 team playoff system former College Football head coach Rick Neuheisel joins the show to discuss which specific teams this would affect the most. And Mike Florio calls in to give us the latest on Aaron Rodgers. What's the end result in his situation?
